Class JUploadContextTestHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • wjhk.jupload2.testhelpers.JUploadContextTestHelper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    wjhk.jupload2.context.JUploadContext

    public class JUploadContextTestHelper
extends Object
implements wjhk.jupload2.context.JUploadContext
    This class is a used as a context, out of real JUpload application. It is used to build contexts for JUnit tests in the JUpload package.
